headline: Assessing CSX (CSX) Valuation After Recent Share Price Momentum And Infrastructure Progress
summary: Why CSX Stock Is Drawing Attention Now CSX (CSX) is back on many investors' screens after a period of strong recent returns, prompting a closer look at how its rail focused freight business and current valuation metrics fit into portfolios. headline: CSX Inks $670M Deal With Wabtec to Expand Fleet Modernization
summary: CSX signs a $670M deal with Wabtec to buy 100 locomotives and modernize 50 units, which boosts fuel efficiency, reliability and long-term network performance.
